          <div id="News">
            <div id="myHeader" style="background-color: #fed780;padding: 20px;margin: 10px;">
              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">News</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">We'd like to offer congratulations to our features editor Larissa Nolan who celebrated her wedding to Conor McManamly in March. Never one to miss a good story opportunity, we look forward to reading about Larissa and Conor's honeymoon tourism adventures in the Florida Keys in an upcoming travel feature! No pun intended but there were stunning jumps across the Cheltenham week on both the Irish Daily Star and Irish Mirror on both titles for the week. More importantly there were great papers all week from front to back pages for those who bought them. Not least in the top coverage of Ireland's triumphant Grand Slam week. Well done too to political correspondent Louise Burne who did a great job as our woman in Washington this year for the St Patrick's Day White House festivities. Top class reporting online and in print when she wasn't popping up all over the airwaves! 
<br>Thanks and well done to all the editorial teams for great coverage. 
               <br> Congratulations to Justin Kernoghan and Mick O'Neill for being shortlisted for the AIB Press Photographer Association of Ireland (PPAI) awards held in Dublin on the 3rd of March. Justin Kernoghan, a Belfast-based photographer, covers a wide range of news and features across Northern Ireland for the Daily Mirror, Irish Star, and Belfast Live. Mick O'Neill has had several front-page images published in the Irish Mirror and Irish Star over the past two years. We can't wait to see what they'll achieve next!

</p>
              <img src=https://github.com/jamesleahyreachplc/TheLoop/blob/April-Loop/News%201.jpg?raw=true style="width:29%;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;">
               <img src=https://github.com/jamesleahyreachplc/TheLoop/blob/April-Loop/News%202.jpg?raw=true style="width:68%;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;">
