          <div id="Commercial">
            <div id="myHeader" style="background-color: #fed780;padding: 20px;margin: 10px;">
              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">Commercial</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">The commercial team has had a positive start to the quarter. They have been actively engaging with agency partners and showcasing their expertise by presenting at various awards. One such event was the "Knowing Me, Knowing You" event where they managed to walk away with two lucrative briefs. The team was thrilled to have the opportunity to build long-lasting relationships with clients.
<br>Furthermore, during the Cheltenham week, all bookies including Boyles, Betfair, William Hill & LiveScore were heavily active on digital, which was a fantastic sight to see. The cherry on top of all this great news was the announcement that the commercial team has won a year-long Sky partnership from Off the Ball.
<br>Did you know that news is still a beloved medium for adults? According to NewsBrands Ireland, 82% of adults read a print or online title every week. News lovers are particularly attentive to newspaper and online ads, with an 18% higher likelihood of paying most attention to them compared to the average adult. Newspapers and online ads are ranked among the top three mediums for attention and purchase decisions. NewsBrands Ireland has even launched a new print and digital campaign to celebrate this enduring love for news! More details here 
<a href="https://www.newsbrandsireland.ie/" style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"><b>newsbrandsireland.ie</b></a>
              </p>

