            <div id="myHeader" style="background-color: #fed780;padding: 20px;margin: 10px;">
              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">5 minutes with...</h1>
              <h2 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"> Ryan Editor of <a href="http://irishstar.com/" style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"><b>IrishStar.com</b></a></h2>
              
              <img src=https://github.com/jamesleahyreachplc/TheLoop/blob/April-Loop/Ryan%20Smith%20.jpeg?raw=true style="width:20%;">

<h4 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Tell us About Yourself:</h4>
<p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">I joined Reach back in 2015 and have worked as a reporter and editor at Belfast Live, with a brief sojourn to MyLondon in between. I'm on secondment in New York at the moment where I have a bacon and cream cheese bagel every morning and secondly work on <a href="http://irishstar.com/" style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"><b>IrishStar.com</b></a></p>

<h4 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">What does your role involve:</h4>
<p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">I'm the editor of <a href="http://irishstar.com/" style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"><b>IrishStar.com</b></a> - the company's first US site that launched in February. I lead a team based in the US and in Ireland.</p>
              <img src=https://github.com/jamesleahyreachplc/TheLoop/blob/April-Loop/imac-irishstar.png?raw=true style="width:32%;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;">
              <img src=https://github.com/jamesleahyreachplc/TheLoop/blob/April-Loop/Irish%20Star%20square%20(3).png?raw=true style="width:32%;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;">
              
<h4 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Top 5 dinner guests:</h4>
<p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Bob Dylan, Bono, Bruce Springsteen, Axl Rose and Alistair Bushe for the laughs</p>

<h4 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Last Show you watched:</h4>
<p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">You - no spoilers but I can tell you that there's something not quite right with Joe Goldberg.</p>
              
<h4 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Career if I wasn’t in media:</h4>
<p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">A gardener - my nickname at work is 'Green Fingers'.</p>
              
             <h2 style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"> Happy Birthday Ryan. Enjoy celebrating in NY this weekend.</h2>

