              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">Facilities</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">We're excited to announce that lockers have been installed in the Dublin office! Now you can store your personal belongings, including laptops, in a safe and secure way. Don't forget to bring your own padlock if you wish to make use of them. If you're looking to book a meeting room, all the details can be found right here. 
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LhcrhXOdDXIWudpPvdWlb5Niqx2T0R6p31GRr-kkUKU/edit" style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"><b>Dublin</b></a> 
