          <div id="Inclusion">
            <div id="myHeader" style="background-color: #fed780;padding: 20px;margin: 10px;">
              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">Inclusion</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;"> We'd like to give a huge congratulations to the team at Belfast Live who have been nominated by the public as the most supportive media outlet for the LGBTQ+ community for the GNI Awards! The Belfast Hub got the Easter celebrations started early with a fun-filled day of Easter Bingo, Easter Egg Raffle, and Easter treats on Tuesday the 4th of April, all in aid of the amazing charity Extern which supports people who are homeless or facing homelessness. Meanwhile, Easter cheer has spread to Dublin with Easter eggs, chocolate treats, and hot cross buns!
 </p>
